TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: --Filter ((VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.CLM_LOCK_CD IN ($$CLM_LOCK_CD) AND VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.APC_STAT_CD IN ($$APC_STAT_CD)) OR VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.PRD_ID = $$HOLD_PRD_ID)
